<h1>Estonia will increase the population by 10 million digital citizens</h1>

<figure>
<a href="00b.jpg"><img src="00.jpg"/></a>
</figure>

<p>
Estonia intends to increase the number of its residents by offering electronic citizenship. The program, which started 2 years ago, allows any citizen of the country to open a bank account and a business and manage it remotely. Thus the government hopes to attract 10 million virtual citizens, mostly - entrepreneurs.
</p>

